snippet.title: Marvel's Midnight Suns | "Welcome to the Abbey" Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Abbey, your home to live among the legends. But like most things, there’s more to this place than meets the eye…

Launch your epic adventure among the legendary #MidnightSuns on December 2, 2022.

► Watch the Prequel Shorts: https://2kgam.es/3G3rVLf

► Pre-order now for PS5, Xbox Series X|S, & PC: https://2kgam.es/3TGGad6
► Join the Official Midnight Suns Newsletter and get the exclusive Blade Nightstalker Skin: https://2kgam.es/Nightstalker
► Learn more about the Midnight Suns: https://2kgam.es/3Qdk2V1
